.el .ds Aq '
.TH dnglab-reembed 1  "dnglab-reembed " 
.SH NAME
dnglab\-reembed \- Re\-embed an edited preview JPEG into an existing DNG (preserves raw/metadata)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdnglab\-reembed\fR <\fB\-\-dng\fR> <\fB\-\-preview\fR> [\fB\-\-output\fR] [\fB\-c\fR|\fB\-\-compression\fR] [\fB\-\-ljpeg92\-predictor\fR] [\fB\-\-artist\fR] [\fB\-\-crop\fR] [\fB\-\-dng\-preview\fR] [\fB\-\-dng\-thumbnail\fR] [\fB\-\-embed\-raw\fR] [\fB\-\-compress\fR] [\fB\-f\fR|\fB\-\-override\fR] [\fB\-\-seed\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Re\-embed an edited preview JPEG into an existing DNG (preserves raw/metadata)
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-dng\fR=\fIdng\fR
Existing DNG file to re\-embed preview into
.TP
\fB\-\-preview\fR=\fIpreview\fR
Edited preview JPEG to embed
.TP
\fB\-\-output\fR=\fIoutput\fR
Output DNG path (defaults to overwriting \-\-dng)
.TP
\fB\-c\fR, \fB\-\-compression\fR=\fIcompression\fR [default: lossless]
Compression for raw image
.br

.br
[\fIpossible values: \fRlossless, uncompressed]
.TP
\fB\-\-ljpeg92\-predictor\fR=\fIpredictor\fR [default: 1]
LJPEG\-92 predictor
.TP
\fB\-\-artist\fR=\fIartist\fR
Set the artist tag
.TP
\fB\-\-crop\fR=\fIcrop\fR [default: best]
DNG default crop
.br

.br
[\fIpossible values: \fRbest, activearea, none]
.TP
\fB\-\-dng\-preview\fR=\fIpreview\fR [default: true]
DNG include preview image
.br

.br
[\fIpossible values: \fRtrue, false]
.TP
\fB\-\-dng\-thumbnail\fR=\fIthumbnail\fR [default: true]
DNG include thumbnail image
.br

.br
[\fIpossible values: \fRtrue, false]
.TP
\fB\-\-embed\-raw\fR=\fIembedded\fR [default: true]
Re\-embed the original raw file into DNG
.br

.br
[\fIpossible values: \fRtrue, false]
.TP
\fB\-\-compress\fR
Enable lossless compression (equivalent to \-c)
.TP
\fB\-f\fR, \fB\-\-override\fR
Override existing files
.TP
\fB\-\-seed\fR=\fIseed\fR [default: ]
Deterministic seed for reproducible output (use the same seed as the original conversion)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
